Firefox OS London Meetup
========================


Using Web Activities
--------------------

In this repo you could find the code that we follow in the Firefox OS London meetup group around activities.

This first example will show you how to use other activities defined in the system.

Installation
--------------

For the final result just download the repo
```sh
git clone https://github.com/firefoxos-london-meetup/using-web-activities
```

If you prefer go step by step, there is a release with the skeleton of the app. You can download it from here:

https://github.com/firefoxos-london-meetup/using-web-activities/releases
